206std::vector<RtpExtension> RtpExtension::FilterDuplicateNonEncrypted(
207 const std::vector<RtpExtension>& extensions) {
208 std::vector<RtpExtension> filtered;
209 for (auto extension = extensions.begin(); extension != extensions.end();
210 ++extension) {
211 if (extension->encrypt) {
212 filtered.push_back(*extension);
213 continue;
214 }
215
216 // Only add non-encrypted extension if no encrypted with the same URI
217 // is also present...
218 if (std::any_of(extension + 1, extensions.end(),
219 [&](const RtpExtension& check) {
220 return extension->uri == check.uri;
221 })) {
222 continue;
223 }
224
225 // ...and has not been added before.
226 if (!FindHeaderExtensionByUri(filtered, extension->uri)) {
227 filtered.push_back(*extension);
228 }
229 }
230 return filtered;
